<br>

<div class="row">
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="container">
        <img src="../../../images/4v4+3.jpg" alt="Jane" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
       <h4>Pep Guariola's 4v4+3 drill</h4>
        <p class="title">17 minutes total (5 mins on 1 min break )</p>
       <p><b>Set Up</b>: 12 x 24 yards grid</p>
        <p><b>Players Needed:</b> 11 players, two teams of four and three neutral players. 7 v 4 in posession</p>
        <p><b>Explanation:</b><br> The three neutral players keep posession with the team on the outside. two neutral players placed either end ogf the grid and one in the middle. If/when the team of 4 in the middle win the ball back there is a transational movement in which they maintain possesion with the neutral players and take the outside postion</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjHC36vAdDo" target="_blank"><p><button style="width:250px" class="button">Video <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></button></p></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="../../../images/rondo.jpg" alt="Jane" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
      <h4>Rondo</h4>
        <p class="title">10-25 minutes</p>
       <p><b>Set Up</b>: 10 x 10 yards grid</p>
        <p><b>Players Needed:</b> 5-8 players on the outside and 2 players on the inside of the grid</p>
        <p><b>Explanation:</b> The 5 to 8 players on the outside keep possesion of the ball while the two players in the middle try to regain the ball. The players on the outside should only require two or one touches and off the ball they should always be making passing angles for the man in possesion.</p>
        <center><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VveIVcGtDI0" target="_blank"><p><button style="width:250px" class="button">Video <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></button></p></a></center>
       <br>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="../../../images/dortmunf.jpg" alt="Mike" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h4>Borussia Dortmund's 3rd man running drill</h4>
        <p class="title">10-25 minutes</p>
       <p><b>Set Up</b>:3 cones in a triangle</p>
        <p><b>Players Needed:</b> at least 2 players at each cone</p>
        <p><b>Explanation:</b><br> Player at the first cone plays a pass to the feet of the man on the second cone. They play a one two while the second man on the second cone begins to make the third man run. Once the one two is completed player one plays a through ball to the second man on the second cone making the third man run.This process is repeated going to the third cone back to the first cone and this is repeated</p>
       <center> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=soio0AcYtEE&list=PLWV3d6hqH1xMpTMIMGxD-KXRK-se04rg0&index=4&t=0s" target="_blank"><p><button style="width:250px" class="button">Video <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></button></p></a></center>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="../../../images/juventus.jpg" alt="Mike" style="width:100%">
       <div class="container">
        <h4>Juventus 3v1 and 5v3</h4>
        <p class="title">10-20 minutes</p>
       <p><b>Set Up</b>:A 6x6 yard grid inside a 15x15 yard grid</p>
        <p><b>Players Needed:</b> A team of 3 and a team of5</p>
        <p><b>Explanation:</b><br><p>The Drill starts in the samll grid where a 3v 1 possesion games occurs. When/if the one player regains posession the drill extends to the big grid and now it's a 5 v 3 possesion game. If /when the 3 players win the ball back the drill restarts</p>
        <center><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H-TWT_SsKMg" target="_blank"><p><p><button style="width:250px" class="button">Video <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></button></p></a></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="../../../images/ajax.jpg" alt="Mike" style="width:100%">
       <div class="container">
        <h4>Ajax killer pass</h4>
        <p class="title">10-15 minutes</p>
       <p><b>Set Up</b>: A big grid with 4 attackers on the outside with 3 defenders inside a smaller area with one attcker</p>
        <p><b>Players Needed:</b> 6 attackers 3 defenders</p>
        <p><b>Explanation:</b>Defenders rotate around the cones to prevent the striker obtaining the killer passs. Players on the outside keep the ball until the oppurtunity to play the killer pass arises</p>
        <center><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AfKxLZ_GZdU" target="_blank"><p><button style="width:250px" class="button">Video <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></button></p></a></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

